Text: Awesome collection.  I remember reading the real deal back in the late 70's and this upload brings back those happy memories...

Glad I could help.  For me nostalgia porn is always going to be Hometown Hunnies and a very little known one called Fireworks about a male whorehouse.  Those were the first two VHS tapes I "borrowed" from my dad

wow some of these are really impressive.

thanks.
